/.premium/my-daughters-dont-know-theyre-jewish-and-certainly-not-how-dangerous-that-is/0000018e-c88a-d39c-a98e-dabb1fe40000</link><description>我们看地图，他们问那个小国家是什么。 “这是以色列，是你们出生的地方，”我告诉他们，也是我在美国学习后希望回到的地方。这里的每个人都走向了另一个方向</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-daughters-dont-know-theyre-jewish-and-certainly-not-how-dangerous-that-is/0000018e-c88a-d39c-a98e-dabb1fe40000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示以色列人对民主和国家安全未来的乐观态度创历史新低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-pessimistic-about-future-of-democracy-in-israel-poll-reveals/0000018e-cd51-dba9-a78e-ef5d1c250000</link><description>以色列民主研究所民意调查显示，以色列的国民情绪再创新低，35%的人表示对该国民主统治的未来持乐观态度，34%的人对国家安全持乐观态度</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 14:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-pessimistic-about-future-of-democracy-in-israel-poll-reveals/0000018e-cd51-dba9-a78e-ef5d1c250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列宣布 2024 年西岸土地将创纪录数量归国有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-has-declared-record-amount-of-west-bank-land-as-state-owned-in-2024/0000018e-c7a2-dd23-a3cf-e7a713c90000</link><description>短短三个月内，数千英亩土地被指定为国有财产，而已划归国有的土地的重新规划也为潜在的定居点建设铺平了道路</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:38:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-has-declared-record-amount-of-west-bank-land-as-state-owned-in-2024/0000018e-c7a2-dd23-a3cf-e7a713c90000</guid></item><item><title>展示暴行：10 月 7 日之后以色列的新视觉景观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/illustrating-atrocity-israels-new-visual-landscape-after-october-7/0000018e-c7dc-dd23-a3cf-e7ddaec70000</link><description>黄丝带、涂鸦、口号和纹身：以色列的街道上充斥着对改变一切的这一天的诠释。作为《国土报》的艺术总监，如何表现恐怖充满了道德和美学的困境</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:42:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/illustrating-atrocity-israels-new-visual-landscape-after-october-7/0000018e-c7dc-dd23-a3cf-e7ddaec70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内政部长与内塔尼亚胡因巴勒斯坦工人发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-versus-netanyahu-theyre-pushing-decisions-down-my-throat/0000018e-cc65-dfbb-ad8f-fe67055e0000</link><description>内政部长摩西·阿贝尔猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡干涉外国工人入境，因为巴勒斯坦工人被禁止，10月7日和加沙战争后数千名外国工人离开，以色列工业严重短缺。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:37:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-versus-netanyahu-theyre-pushing-decisions-down-my-throat/0000018e-cc65-dfbb-ad8f-fe67055e0000</guid></item><item><title>杀害哈马斯领导人的儿子不会破坏协议，但可能会进一步推迟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/killing-of-hamas-leaders-sons-wont-torpedo-deal-but-could-postpone-it-more/0000018e-cca9-df04-adae-edfb62350000</link><description>哈马斯将很难解释为什么对其政治领袖的子孙的袭击掩盖了自战争开始以来它提出的要求，但哈尼亚的地位可能会得到提升</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/killing-of-hamas-leaders-sons-wont-torpedo-deal-but-could-postpone-it-more/0000018e-cca9-df04-adae-edfb62350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列基布兹举行逾越节家宴，恳求释放被扣押在加沙地带的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-kibbutz-sets-up-passover-seder-to-implore-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018e-cc80-df04-adae-edd2ddd00000</link><description>“带回所有人质，让这个夜晚与众不同”：尼尔·奥兹基布兹成员摆出了一张逾越节家宴桌，上面有 36 张椅子，代表仍被关押在加沙的社区人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:20:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.pr