a-pointless-success/0000018e-c904-d1b7-a3af-ef0fb2820000</link><description>如果没有可行的策略来遵循，成功的机动就是：为了机动而机动。事后看来，需要进行更有限的地面进攻，这本来可以减少哈马斯和加沙的损失，但之后会给以色列更多的选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 19:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-maneuver-in-gaza-was-a-pointless-success/0000018e-c904-d1b7-a3af-ef0fb2820000</guid></item></channel></rss>